Title: Starter Scene
Credit: Written with Scriptboard
Author: Scriptboard Example

INT. SMALL KITCHEN - MORNING

A kettle hums on the stove.

MIRA enters, still half asleep, carrying a notebook.

MIRA
Today I am going to write something simple.

She opens the notebook and stares at the blank page.

MIRA
(quietly)
One scene. One decision. That is enough.

The kettle clicks off.

CUT TO:
